{
  "eval": "live_currency",
  "method": "Deterministic probes of a running DKAN dev site over MCP stdio (tools/list + read-only tools/call) plus 3 HTTP probes via curl, compared against expected values pinned from the skill docs' claims. Doc-tripwire regexes guard the claim text itself. No LLM, no writes; the writer session is used for tools/list only.",
