    "mcp_http_path": "/mcp",
    "transport": {
      "ro": "ddev drush dkan-mcp-server:serve --user=mcp_reader",
      "rw": "ddev drush dkan-mcp-server:serve --user=mcp_writer \u2014 tools/list only"
    },
    "protocol": {
      "client": "2025-03-26",
      "server": "2025-11-25"
    },
    "site_fingerprint": {
      "dkan": "4.1.1",
      "drupal": "11.3.11",
      "datasets_total": 10,
      "distributions_total": 13,
      "harvest_plans": 1
    },
    "probes_run": [
      "http.anon",
      "http.basic",
      "http.prm",
      "mcp_ro.call.get_schema_dataset",
      "mcp_ro.call.get_site_status",
      "mcp_ro.call.list_schemas",
      "mcp_ro.tools_list",
      "mcp_rw.tools_list"
    ],
    "caveats": [
      "Snapshot of one pinned dev site (dkan_mcp_server 1.0.x on dkan-site DDEV), not upstream truth; counts will legitimately drift as the module evolves \u2014 that drift is the signal, but expect maintenance.",
      "HTTP posture checks are three shallow probes scoped to the MCP endpoint only (deliberately silent on /api/1/*), not a security audit.",
      "Deterministic = no LLM and stable given fixed site state; the site itself is mutable, so results are dated, not byte-reproducible forever."
    ]
